, 
<figureCitation box="[260,303,1301,1327]" captionStart="FIGURES 4" captionStartId="39.[151,264,1897,1922]" captionTargetBox="[188,1409,181,1867]" captionTargetId="figure@39.[164,1423,166,1884]" captionTargetPageId="39" captionText="FIGURES 4 A–O. Habitus of Coelidiini species, lateral view. A. Calodia deergha sp. nov., male; B. C. keralica sp. nov., male; C &amp; D. C. kodikanelensis Nielson, male and female; E. C. kumari sp. nov., male; F &amp; G. C. neofusca sp. nov., male and female; H &amp; I. C. ostenta (Distant), male and female; J. C. periyari sp. nov., male; K. C. subcrista Nielson, male; L. C. tridenta sp. nov., male; M. Glaberana acuta sp. nov., male; N &amp; O. G. khasiensis (Rao), male and female." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3366552/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">4 A</figureCitation>
