<figureCitation box="[314,356,1301,1327]" captionStart="FIGURES 7" captionStartId="42.[151,264,1892,1917]" captionTargetBox="[175,1425,310,1744]" captionTargetId="figure@42.[151,1435,264,1750]" captionTargetPageId="42" captionText="FIGURES 7 A–P. Faces of Coelidiini species. A. Calodia deergha sp. nov., male; B. C. keralica sp. nov., male; C &amp; D. C. kodikanelensis Nielson, male and female; E. C. kumari sp. nov., male; F &amp; G. C. neofusca sp. nov., male and female; H &amp; I. C. ostenta (Distant), male and female; J. C. periyari sp. nov., male; K. C. subcrista Nielson, male; L. C. tridenta sp. nov., male; M. Glaberana acuta sp. nov., Male; N &amp; O. G. khasiensis (Rao), male and female. P. Glaberana purva sp. nov., male." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3366558/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">7 A</figureCitation>
