<figureCitation box="[367,395,1300,1327]" captionStart="FIGURES 15" captionStartId="50.[151,264,1968,1993]" captionTargetBox="[183,1406,166,1916]" captionTargetId="figure@50.[163,1425,166,1948]" captionTargetPageId="50" captionText="FIGURES 15 A–H. Calodia deergha sp. nov., male genitalia. A &amp; B. Aedeagus, dorsal view; C &amp; D. Aedeagus, lateral view; E. Subgenital plate, dorsal view; F. Style, dorsal view; G. Connective, dorsal view; H. Pygofer, lateral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3366574/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">15</figureCitation>
A–H.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1437,1373,1867]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">
<emphasis box="[151,209,1373,1399]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">
<collectingRegion box="[151,209,1373,1399]" country="Maldives" name="Maale" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Male</collectingRegion>
</emphasis>
. Head ochraceous, ocelli black; eyes brown; pronotum and mesonotum black with posterior margin paler; forewings ochraceous; thoracic sternites and pleurites largely black with broad ochraceous margins.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1437,1373,1867]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">
<emphasis box="[199,373,1445,1471]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">
<collectingRegion box="[199,257,1445,1471]" country="Maldives" name="Maale" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Male</collectingRegion>
genitalia.
</emphasis>
Pygofer with digitate caudoventral process, without caudodorsal process, small lobe on caudodorsal margin (
<figureCitation box="[352,466,1480,1507]" captionStart="FIGURES 15" captionStartId="50.[151,264,1968,1993]" captionTargetBox="[183,1406,166,1916]" captionTargetId="figure@50.[163,1425,166,1948]" captionTargetPageId="50" captionText="FIGURES 15 A–H. Calodia deergha sp. nov., male genitalia. A &amp; B. Aedeagus, dorsal view; C &amp; D. Aedeagus, lateral view; E. Subgenital plate, dorsal view; F. Style, dorsal view; G. Connective, dorsal view; H. Pygofer, lateral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3366574/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Fig. 15 H</figureCitation>
). Subgenital plate of uniform width, slightly broader medially and basally, with short setae (15 E). Style short, broad basally (
<figureCitation box="[604,711,1516,1543]" captionStart="FIGURES 15" captionStartId="50.[151,264,1968,1993]" captionTargetBox="[183,1406,166,1916]" captionTargetId="figure@50.[163,1425,166,1948]" captionTargetPageId="50" captionText="FIGURES 15 A–H. Calodia deergha sp. nov., male genitalia. A &amp; B. Aedeagus, dorsal view; C &amp; D. Aedeagus, lateral view; E. Subgenital plate, dorsal view; F. Style, dorsal view; G. Connective, dorsal view; H. Pygofer, lateral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3366574/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Fig. 15 F</figureCitation>
). Connective as long as wide at base (
<figureCitation box="[1142,1255,1516,1543]" captionStart="FIGURES 15" captionStartId="50.[151,264,1968,1993]" captionTargetBox="[183,1406,166,1916]" captionTargetId="figure@50.[163,1425,166,1948]" captionTargetPageId="50" captionText="FIGURES 15 A–H. Calodia deergha sp. nov., male genitalia. A &amp; B. Aedeagus, dorsal view; C &amp; D. Aedeagus, lateral view; E. Subgenital plate, dorsal view; F. Style, dorsal view; G. Connective, dorsal view; H. Pygofer, lateral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3366574/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Fig. 15 G</figureCitation>
). Aedeagus narrowed at apical half in lateral view, with two subapical, glabrous spine-like processes, distal process 
<date box="[1275,1303,1553,1579]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">2x</date>
longer than the proximal process, gonopore arising distad of base of proximal process (
<figureCitation box="[993,1084,1588,1615]" captionStart="FIGURES 15" captionStartId="50.[151,264,1968,1993]" captionTargetBox="[183,1406,166,1916]" captionTargetId="figure@50.[163,1425,166,1948]" captionTargetPageId="50" captionText="FIGURES 15 A–H. Calodia deergha sp. nov., male genitalia. A &amp; B. Aedeagus, dorsal view; C &amp; D. Aedeagus, lateral view; E. Subgenital plate, dorsal view; F. Style, dorsal view; G. Connective, dorsal view; H. Pygofer, lateral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3366574/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Figs. 15</figureCitation>
A–D).
</paragraph>
